CONTENTS            

This is the IBIS model for Cypress part CY7C65632/34/42
This is the low-power version of Cypress's USB 2 compliant Hub.    

VERIFICATION            

This model was syntax checked with Hyperlynx 4.1 visual IBIS editor.  

There are several monotonicity warnings in this file due to the subtraction of
the clamp data from the pullup/pulldown curves; this result is expected.
The USB ground clamp data has extreme current warnings in this file; system 
simulation run and passed to ensure this doesn't cause any issues.

VERSION HISTORY           

1.0 - 2012 February 22 Generated HX2VL IBIS model

 Silicon Model Information         
 -------------------------           
 **All silicon based measurements were performed on TYPICAL silicon. MIN and 
 MAX values represent +/-20% of the TYPICAL silicon measurement****   

 Pullup and Pulldown curves still have the simulation based clamp data in them
 Reference resistor RREF = 650ohm
  

QUESTIONS?             

 If there are any additional questions or concerns about using this  
 "model," please create a technical support case at www.cypress.com/support    
 or call the technical support line at 1-800-541-4736 option 8   
